description: Professional architectural blueprint for a 1200 Square Feet house with For a 3BHK floor plan on a 1,200 square feet plot in Chennai, prioritize efficient space utilization with climate-responsive design. Include a spacious living room, dining area, and modular kitchen with good ventilation. Ensure three well-ventilated bedrooms (one master with attached bath), two or three bathrooms, and a utility area. Incorporate natural lighting and cross-ventilation to suit Chennai’s climate. Provide parking for one vehicle and a small garden or sit-out. Maintain privacy between public and private spaces. Use eco-friendly materials and provisions for rainwater harvesting and solar energy to enhance sustainability within the INR 5,000,000 budget.
